00030  SUBROUTINE VtkDump
00031 
00032 ! Common Variables
00033  USE Ntypes,      ONLY : DBL
00034  USE Domain
00035  USE FluidParams, ONLY : alpha, kappa, phi, phiStar2, phiStar4
00036  USE LBMParams,   ONLY : Cs_sq, g
00037  USE MPI
00038  IMPLICIT NONE
00039 
00040 ! Required functions
00041  CHARACTER(12) :: filer
00042 
00043 ! Local Variables
00044  INTEGER :: i, j, k, ie, iw, jn, js, kt, kb
00045  INTEGER :: IO_ERR, MPI_ERR
00046  REAL(KIND = DBL) :: ux, uy, uz, phin, phin2, pressure, rhon, invRhon
00047  REAL(KIND = DBL) :: gradPhiX, gradPhiY, gradPhiZ, gradPhiSq, lapPhi
00048  REAL(KIND = DBL) :: in00, in01, in02, in03, in04, in05, in06, in07, in08, in09
00049  REAL(KIND = DBL) :: in10, in11, in12, in13, in14, in15, in16, in17, in18
00050  CHARACTER(12) :: filer1
00051  CHARACTER(16) :: fmtd1, fmtd3
00052  CHARACTER(20) :: filer2
00053 
00054 
00055 ! Set output files formats and names
00056  fmtd1 = '(1(ES21.11E3))'
00057  fmtd3 = '(3(ES21.11E3))'
00058  filer1 = filer()
00059  filer2 = "DATA"//filer1(1:12)//".vtk"
00060 
00061  OPEN(UNIT = 12, FILE = filer2, STATUS = "NEW", POSITION = "APPEND", &
00062       IOSTAT = IO_ERR)
00063  IF ( IO_ERR == 0 ) THEN
00064    WRITE(12,'(A)')"# vtk DataFile Version 2.0"
00065    WRITE(12,'(A)')"MP-LABS v1.0"
00066    WRITE(12,'(A)')"ASCII"
00067    WRITE(12,*)
00068    WRITE(12,'(A)')"DATASET STRUCTURED_POINTS"
00069    WRITE(12,*)"DIMENSIONS",NPX,NPY,NPZ
00070    WRITE(12,*)"ORIGIN",xl,yl,zl
00071    WRITE(12,*)"SPACING",xjump,xjump,xjump
00072    WRITE(12,*)
00073    WRITE(12,*)"POINT_DATA",NPX*NPY*NPZ
00074    WRITE(12,*)
00075    WRITE(12,'(A)')"SCALARS Phi double"
00076    WRITE(12,'(A)')"LOOKUP_TABLE default"
00077    DO k = zl, zu, xjump
00078       DO j = yl, yu, xjump
00079          DO i = xl, xu, xjump
00080             WRITE(UNIT = 12,FMT = fmtd1)phi(i,j,k)
00081          END DO
00082       END DO
00083    END DO
00084    WRITE(12,*)
00085    WRITE(12,'(A)')"SCALARS Pressure double"
00086    WRITE(12,'(A)')"LOOKUP_TABLE default"
00087    DO k = zl, zu, xjump
00088       DO j = yl, yu, xjump
00089          DO i = xl, xu, xjump
00090 
00091             rhon  = SUM( g(i,j,k,:,now) )
00092             phin  = phi(i,j,k)
00093             phin2 = phin*phin
00094 
00095 ! Identify neighbours
00096             ie = ni(i,j,k,1)
00097             iw = ni(i,j,k,2)
00098             jn = ni(i,j,k,3)
00099             js = ni(i,j,k,4)
00100             kt = ni(i,j,k,5)
00101             kb = ni(i,j,k,6)
00102 
00103 ! Nodal values of the order parameter
00104             in00 = phi(i ,j ,k )
00105             in01 = phi(ie,j ,k )
00106             in02 = phi(iw,j ,k )
00107             in03 = phi(i ,jn,k )
00108             in04 = phi(i ,js,k )
00109             in05 = phi(i ,j ,kt)
00110             in06 = phi(i ,j ,kb)
00111             in07 = phi(ie,jn,k )
00112             in08 = phi(iw,js,k )
00113             in09 = phi(ie,js,k )
00114             in10 = phi(iw,jn,k )
00115             in11 = phi(ie,j ,kt)
00116             in12 = phi(iw,j ,kb)
00117             in13 = phi(ie,j ,kb)
00118             in14 = phi(iw,j ,kt)
00119             in15 = phi(i ,jn,kt)
00120             in16 = phi(i ,js,kb)
00121             in17 = phi(i ,jn,kb)
00122             in18 = phi(i ,js,kt)
00123 
00124 ! Laplacian of the order parameter
00125             lapPhi = ( in07 + in08 + in09 + in10 + in11 + in12 + in13 + in14 &
00126                    + in15 + in16 + in17 + in18 + 2.0D0*( in01 + in02 + in03  &
00127                    + in04 + in05 + in06 - 12.D0*in00 ) )*inv6
00128 
00129 ! Components of the order parameter gradient
00130             gradPhiX  = ( 2.0D0*( in01 - in02 ) + in07 - in08 + in09 - in10 &
00131                       + in11 - in12 + in13 - in14 )*inv12
00132 
00133             gradPhiY  = ( 2.0D0*( in03 - in04 ) + in07 - in08 + in10 - in09 &
00134                       + in15 - in16 + in17 - in18 )*inv12
00135 
00136             gradPhiZ  = ( 2.0D0*( in05 - in06 ) + in11 - in12 + in14 - in13 &
00137                       + in15 - in16 + in18 - in17 )*inv12
00138 
00139             gradPhiSq = gradPhiX*gradPhiX + gradPhiY*gradPhiY + gradPhiZ*gradPhiZ
00140 
00141 ! Calculate the pressure
00142             pressure = alpha*( phin2*( 3.D0*phin2 - 2.D0*phiStar2 ) - phiStar4 ) &
00143                      - kappa*( phin*lapPhi - 0.5D0*gradPhiSq ) + Cs_sq*rhon
00144 
00145             WRITE(UNIT = 12,FMT = fmtd1)pressure
00146          END DO
00147       END DO
00148    END DO
00149    WRITE(12,*)
00150    WRITE(12,'(A)')"VECTORS Velocity double"
00151    DO k = zl, zu, xjump
00152       DO j = yl, yu, xjump
00153          DO i = xl, xu, xjump
00154 
00155            rhon = SUM( g(i,j,k,:,now) )
00156            invRhon = 1.D0/rhon
00157 
00158            ux = ( g(i,j,k, 1,now) - g(i,j,k, 2,now) + g(i,j,k, 7,now) &
00159               -   g(i,j,k, 8,now) + g(i,j,k, 9,now) - g(i,j,k,10,now) &
00160               +   g(i,j,k,11,now) - g(i,j,k,12,now) + g(i,j,k,13,now) &
00161               - g(i,j,k,14,now) )*invRhon
00162 
00163            uy = ( g(i,j,k, 3,now) - g(i,j,k, 4,now) + g(i,j,k, 7,now) &
00164               -   g(i,j,k, 8,now) - g(i,j,k, 9,now) + g(i,j,k,10,now) &
00165               +   g(i,j,k,15,now) - g(i,j,k,16,now) + g(i,j,k,17,now) &
00166               - g(i,j,k,18,now) )*invRhon
00167 
00168            uz = ( g(i,j,k, 5,now) - g(i,j,k, 6,now) + g(i,j,k,11,now) &
00169               -   g(i,j,k,12,now) - g(i,j,k,13,now) + g(i,j,k,14,now) &
00170               +   g(i,j,k,15,now) - g(i,j,k,16,now) - g(i,j,k,17,now) &
00171               + g(i,j,k,18,now) )*invRhon
00172 
00173             WRITE(UNIT = 12,FMT = fmtd3)ux,uy,uz
00174          END DO
00175       END DO
00176    END DO
00177    CLOSE(UNIT = 12)
00178  ELSE
00179    CALL MemAlloc(2)
00180    CALL MPI_FINALIZE(MPI_ERR)
00181    STOP "Error: Unable to open output vtk file."
00182  END IF
00183 
00184  RETURN
00185  END SUBROUTINE VtkDump
